      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this motorcar\u2014from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments\u2014has been maintained to exacting standards. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a specimen of unrivaled quality and documented mechanical integrity. We invite serious inquiries for this showroom-quality masterpiece.",
