      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I'm so sad to let this beauty go. It's been kept in absolutely incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've totally babied this car, keeping it spotless and always tucked away in the garage. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the dealership headache, you've found it. It's such a dream to drive, and I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
